{"tid":860777,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【不動嶼山】巨型橫額現坪洲 關注組籲周日遊行反填海","createTime":"2018-10-13T15:05:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-13T21:58:59.000Z","uid":25558,"like":24,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9a8b730d13ce8182dc3ddaa2262f7167fa3453b5","tid":860777,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:05:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181013/58791241\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181013%2F58791241&d=Dr3og%2FehezBAl2htW82PDMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=6bb99e8b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181013%2F58791241&h=80260baa\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20181013/58791241</a><br />\n<br />\n【不動嶼山】巨型橫額現坪洲 關注組籲周日遊行反填海<br />\n<br />\n1小時前<br />\n即時要聞<br />\n <br />\n【新增影片】<br />\n<br />\n守護大嶼聯盟聯同坪洲填海關注組及當地居民，今日下午在坪洲南灣掛起巨幅橫額，表達反對大規模填海的立場。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n坪洲填海關注組表示，施政報告提出的「明日大嶼」計劃將對交椅洲﹑周公島﹑坪洲及喜靈洲等構成嚴重影響。當中周公島已在2015年定為「具特殊科學價值地點」的重要生態保護地區，而坪洲則是當中唯一一個有數千居民的社區。<br />\n<br />\n關注組對當局將填海規模升級，直接危害當地居民，表示憤怒。他呼籲坪洲居民參予守護大嶼聯盟在周日（14日）發起的遊行表達反對聲音。<br />\n<br />\n據了解，坪洲填海關注組成立於2012年初，當時政府進行填海諮詢，選址包括坪洲－喜靈洲連島方案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n立會補選新聞，《蘋果》一網睇晒<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/appledaily1125\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2Fappledaily1125&d=Dr3og%2FehezBAl2htW82PDMP%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=fe978489\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/appledaily1125</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181013/large/1539425902_441c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181013%2Flarge%2F1539425902_441c.jpg&h=af6f43e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n守護大嶼聯盟提供圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181013/large/1539426175_e2a7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181013%2Flarge%2F1539426175_e2a7.jpg&h=468059e1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n坪洲填海關注組表示，「明日大嶼」計劃將對交椅洲（圖）﹑周公島﹑坪洲及喜靈洲等造成嚴重影響。守護大嶼聯盟提供"},{"pid":"589bda7cd9a6abcdfd78ce31952ca4a46f6a074a","tid":860777,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:22:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1a2c7ecd789dfec81ad9a9cc65b0dab57afdf78","tid":860777,"uid":205462,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T15:34:03.000Z","msg":"政府: 我睇你唔到，我睇你唔到"},{"pid":"263c20a6cb2f1acbf806d1dea2e1b8a657ea2bd2","tid":860777,"uid":22624,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T17:52:19.000Z","msg":"不動嶼山<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae881ffaed8dc6395a9335e80d6eb26a12d2f1b3","tid":860777,"uid":14422,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T18:09:13.000Z","msg":"自撚私到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"81aafac5de19e75f79ad977f9908f90aedc51c0a","tid":860777,"uid":153689,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-13T21:58:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}